requirements.text:
Replace the existing Google Ads tracking tag in frontend/index.html with the new tracking code. Update the gtag.js script src from 'https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=AW-17968689708' to 'https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=AW-17969512168', and update the gtag('config', 'AW-17968689708') call to gtag('config', 'AW-17969512168'). The complete replacement script block is:

<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
<script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=AW-17969512168"></script>
<script>
  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
  gtag('js', new Date());
  gtag('config', 'AW-17969512168');
</script>

Keep the script placement in the <head> section before the closing </head> tag, maintaining async loading.
